{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":23025,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":3851,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"父权的压迫","timestamp":1592892065,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23029,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":3851,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我恐怕一辈子付不起","timestamp":1592892084,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23048,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":3851,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Bob: 来打拳","timestamp":1592892132,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23064,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":3851,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"个人感觉收彩礼是在卖自己。\n上大学以前没听说过彩礼，上大学之后才知道，自己绝不会要更不会收，支持小家庭的启动资金和卖儿鬻女混为一谈很恶心。","timestamp":1592892168,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23066,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":3851,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 可否详细的叙述","timestamp":1592892174,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23099,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":3851,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"收了低声下气，不如不收，要给的话两方父母都给差不多的启动资金，要么都别给","timestamp":1592892275,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23112,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":3851,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: （主要因为现在收彩礼的主体和用途现在都不怎么明确，甚至有女方家庭主张彩礼的","timestamp":1592892313,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23127,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":3851,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: 彩礼是男方给女方，当然是女方家庭主张，嫁妆是女方出的","timestamp":1592892353,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23130,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":3851,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"不觉得是卖自己，合理范围内的，双方达成一致的就行。虽说不能用钱衡量感情，但现实生活中能力范围内的钱都不愿意出，又能对你有多好... ","timestamp":1592892367,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23136,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":3851,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"来自没有彩礼习俗地区，上大学被江浙沪彩礼吓尿","timestamp":1592892380,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23138,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":3851,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"当然这笔钱是要给女方的，那种嫁女儿收彩礼给儿子娶媳妇的我坚决反对","timestamp":1592892400,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23140,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":3851,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: （感觉更像是有人借这种陋习在浑水摸鱼，给自己捞更多的利益","timestamp":1592892405,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23173,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":3851,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"他们未必有性别平等/父权这类的上位概念或受影响，只是多了个恰拦钱的手段（来自无彩礼地区，虚空打靶石锤（","timestamp":1592892522,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23176,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Hans","permissions":["report"],"pid":3851,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Carol: 顶顶","timestamp":1592892539,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23177,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":3851,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: 彩礼就是父权家庭卖女儿，在彩礼制度下女性作为生育机器从原生家庭被卖到夫家，这份钱再用于原生家庭从别家买媳妇","timestamp":1592892545,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23182,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":3851,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: 确实，表妹最近结婚，他爸没有再婚后基本没管她，读书工作全是我家这边安排的，她继母要求男方出彩礼。可把我恶心坏了","timestamp":1592892566,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23187,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":3851,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: 彩礼会弱化女性在新家庭中的地位，使其作为附属存在","timestamp":1592892589,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23328,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":3851,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"无彩礼地区＋1，感觉自己在隔空打拳……","timestamp":1592893082,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":3,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":3851,"reply":18,"tag":null,"text":"如何看待彩礼？","timestamp":1592892037,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782585,"url":"","vote":{}}}